					<div style="float:left;"><strong class="xar-sub">Subject:<a name="85807" href="http://www.ldonline.org/xarbb/topic/14152#85807">Re:  Petition Against Reauthorization of NCLB Act
</a></strong></div>
					<div style="clear: both;"></div>
				</div>
				<div style="clear: left;">
															<p>Discussion of NCLB is in the news now. Lots of thought is being given as to whether states must continue to test, test, test. Some ideas to make states' participation in NCLB voluntary.</p>
<p>28,000+ persons have signed the petition at <a href="http://www.petitiononline.com/1teacher/petition.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">www.petitiononline.com/1teacher/petition.html</a> .</p>
<p>Anita learntoreadnow</p>
